# block-string-indicator-fallback

## Input

```
a |+text
b >-stuff
c | not blank

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..33
  ENTRY@0..9
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    LINE_STRING@2..8
      STRING@2..8 "|+text"
    NEWLINE@8..9 "\n"
  ENTRY@9..19
    WORD_KEY@9..10
      WORD@9..10 "b"
    SPACE@10..11 " "
    LINE_STRING@11..18
      STRING@11..18 ">-stuff"
    NEWLINE@18..19 "\n"
  ENTRY@19..33
    WORD_KEY@19..20
      WORD@19..20 "c"
    SPACE@20..21 " "
    LINE_STRING@21..32
      STRING@21..32 "| not blank"
    NEWLINE@32..33 "\n"
```

